Author: Zealeum
Title: [ANN|TOKEN SALE] ZEALEUM - Blockchain-Based Health & Wellness Platform
Body: You can sell your anonymous health & wellness data on the platform to interested parties in order to earn ZEAL, you can attend a sponsored Zealeum event such as a marathon and scan a QR code on site to earn ZEAL, you can earn tokens by visiting a local gym that is partnered with Zealeum (announcements to be made shortly on partnerships).  There will be other ways to earn ZEAL such as participating in surveys, filling out PROs, and more. In short, Zealeum will allow users to earn cryptocurrencies with their body. By being healthy, tracking health, or making healthy decisions.

Author: Zealeum
Title: [ANN|TOKEN SALE] ZEALEUM - Blockchain-Based Health & Wellness Platform
Body: At the moment, there are no platforms doing exactly what Zealeum does, however there are projects which are aiming to reward users for their healthy activities in a similar fashion to the way Zealeum does! We believe that Zealeum is the full package, and we expect to positively impact several facets of the health and wellness industry by connecting them to professionals who can serve their needs, and creating an ecosystem which benefits all participants. Check out www.zealeum.life for more!
